A dynamic, chaotic illustration of a wizard, drenched in crimson and gold sparks, smashing a massive, ornate artifact with a glowing fist. Around him, shattered fragments of the artifact float in a swirling vortex of energy, with a distressed and enraged expression on the wizard's face.  Style:  Painterly, dramatic lighting, slightly distressed brushstrokes reminiscent of an old illustration, KOTH SMASH! effect radiating outwards.